sentences: Cecilia Arizti Sobrino (28 October 1856 â€“ 30 June 1930) was a Cuban composer, pianist and music educator.
Cecilia Arizti was born in La Loma del Angel, Havana, the daughter of pianist Fernando Arizti and his wife Teresa Sobrino.
After completing her studies, Arizti performed as a concert pianist in Cuba and the United States.
